Online HW 1 Extra Credit b.) Solution

-2y+z+6x=29
-z+2y-1=0
8y+4x-2z=24

`[[6,-2,1],[0,2,-1],[4,8,-2]] [[x],[y],[z]]=[[29],[1],[24]]`

 `D=|[6,-2,1],[0,2,-1],[4,8,-2]|=6C_11+0C_21+4C_31=6|[2,-1],[8,-2]|-0|[-2,1],[8,-2]|+6|[-2,1],[2,-1]|=6(-4-8)=6*4=24`

`C_12=-|[2,-1],[8,-2]|=-4, C_22=|[6,1],[4,-2]|=-16, C_32=-|[6,1],[0,-1]|=6`

`C_13=|[0,2],[4,8]|=-8, C_23=-|[6,-2],[4,8]|=-56, C_33=|[6,-2],[0,2]|=12`
`bbA^-1=1/D[[C_11,C_12,C_13],[C_21,C_22,C_23],[C_31,C_32,C_33]]^T=1/d[[C_11,C_21,C_31],[C_12,C_22,C_32],[C_13,C_23,C_33]]=1/24[[4,4,0],[-4,-16,6],[-8,-56,12]]=[[1/6,1/6,0],[-1/6,-2/3,1/4],[-1/3,-7/3,1/2]]`
